Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ButtonListener
    The Button Listener page sets the functionality of buttons pressed to start a new lesson or change the current lesson.
    DisplayCharacters
    The DisplayCharacters class alters the display properties (colour, font) of the characters that the user inputs.
    Lesson
    The Lesson class constructs the UI page that displays the lesson characters and accepts user input.
    MakeResults
    The MakeResults class constructs the UI page that displays the user's results of the selected lesson.
    Parser
    The Parser class accepts a string (a file name) and parses it, returning the contents of the file as a string to be used in the GUI.
    Results
    The Results class allows the makeResults class to be called and assists in the creation of the final results page.
    Scheduler
    The Scheduler class runs a timer as a user completes a lesson, and calculates as well as displays the accuracy, speed, and time on the screen.
    SelectionPage
    The SelectionPage class builds and runs the frame for the Lesson Selection page
    UserInput
    The UserInput class accepts user input and compares all the inputed characters to the characters in the lesson.
